casebody.data:
Bradley BEERS, Petitioner,
v.
William P. BARR, Attorney General, et al. No. 19-864. Supreme Court of the United States. May 18, 2020

On petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the *2759Third Circuit. Petition for writ of certiorari granted. Judgment vacated, and case remanded to the United States Court of Appeals for the Third Circuit with instructions to dismiss the case as moot. See United States v. Munsingwear, Inc. , 340 U.S. 36 (1950).
